---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../../css/services.css";
---

<Layout
  title="Education & Training | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional IT education and training services in the UAE. We offer corporate training programs in software development, cloud computing, cybersecurity, and emerging technologies."
  path="/services/education-training/"
  image="/img/og-education.jpg"
>
  <section class="service-content" id="education-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2 class="service-title">Education & Training</h2>
      <p>
        In the rapidly evolving technology landscape, continuous learning is essential for business success. 
        GeneralSoft offers comprehensive IT education and training programs designed to upskill your workforce 
        and keep your team at the cutting edge of technology. Based in the UAE, our training programs combine 
        theoretical knowledge with hands-on practical experience.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you need to train your development team on the latest frameworks, introduce your staff to cloud 
        computing, or build cybersecurity awareness across your organization, we design customized training 
        curricula that match your specific goals and skill levels.
      </p>

      <h3>Training Programs</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Software Development</h4>
          <p>Full-stack development, modern frameworks, mobile app development, and best practices in coding and architecture.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Cloud Computing</h4>
          <p>AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud training covering architecture, deployment, security, and cost optimization.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Cybersecurity</h4>
          <p>Security awareness, ethical hacking, penetration testing, and compliance training for your team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-box">
          <h4>Emerging Technologies</h4>
          <p>AI and machine learning, IoT, blockchain, and data science training programs for forward-thinking organizations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>Why Choose Our Training</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Instructor-led sessions with real-world project experience</li>
        <li>Customized curriculum tailored to your industry and skill level</li>
        <li>Flexible delivery: on-site, remote, or hybrid</li>
        <li>Post-training support and learning resources</li>
        <li>Certification preparation for industry-recognized credentials</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Projects Proof Section -->
      <div class="projects-proof">
        <h3>Proven Training Delivery — Projects Completed</h3>
        <p>
          Our training portfolio includes university-level instruction,
          corporate knowledge transfer, and professional certification programs.
        </p>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Management of Technology & Innovation — ITU Punjab</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Dec 2019 – Apr 2022</span>
            <span class="role">Instructor</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Taught undergraduate and graduate business administration students,
            as well as executive classes, a 3 to 6 credit course on Management
            of Technology and Innovation. The course covered technology
            strategy, innovation management, digital transformation, and the
            intersection of business and technology.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">University Teaching</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Technology Management</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Innovation</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Executive Education</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>BizTalk Knowledge Transfer — 40+ Training Sessions</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Feb 2015 – Dec 2015</span>
            <span class="role">Lead Developer & Trainer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Delivered 40+ recorded web training sessions over Skype for
            Business, each approximately one hour, streamed to customer
            personnel worldwide. Topics included BizTalk 2013 R2 migration,
            zero-touch deployment with TFS/Octopus Deploy, SAP integration with
            SSO (Azure/OAuth), and enterprise integration best practices.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">BizTalk 2013 R2</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Knowledge Transfer</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SAP</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Azure</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Octopus Deploy</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Enterprise Content Management Training Manual</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">Jun 2007 – Aug 2007</span>
            <span class="role">Architect & Lead Developer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Authored a comprehensive 390-page training manual for an enterprise
            content management system serving 22,000+ employees in the
            hospitality industry. The manual covered system architecture,
            content lifecycle management, compliance workflows, and
            administrative procedures.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Technical Writing</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Training Documentation</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">SharePoint ECM</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="project-card">
          <h4>Academic Lectures — History of Programming & TCP/IP</h4>
          <div class="project-meta">
            <span class="date">1997 – 2001</span>
            <span class="role">Guest Lecturer</span>
          </div>
          <p>
            Delivered a series of lectures on the History of Programming at
            California State University, Sacramento. Gave an IEEE-sponsored
            lecture on Data Communication at FAST, and a seminar on "Insight
            into TCP/IP" at Punjab University. Presented a comparative lecture
            on "J2EE versus .Net" at WOW Sacramento.
          </p>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span class="tech-tag">Academic Lecture</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">TCP/IP</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">Programming History</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">J2EE</span>
            <span class="tech-tag">.NET</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Common questions about our training programs in the UAE.</p>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <details>
            <summary>Do you offer training for beginners?</summary>
            <p>Yes. We assess each participant's current skill level and design programs that accommodate beginners through advanced practitioners.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>Can training be conducted at our office?</summary>
            <p>Absolutely. We offer on-site training at your location anywhere in the UAE, as well as remote and hybrid options.</p>
          </details>
          <details>
            <summary>How long are typical training programs?</summary>
            <p>Programs range from one-day workshops to multi-week comprehensive courses, depending on your objectives and depth of coverage required.</p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-content">
        <h2>Invest in Your Team's Growth</h2>
        <p>Contact us to discuss your training needs and create a customized learning program for your organization.</p>
        <div class="contact-info">
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <a href="/en/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br />Get in touch</a>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-item">
            <div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
